---
title: Chicken & Waffles with Hot Sauce & Red Pepper Butter
description: Chicken and waffles is comfort food at its finest, and this version adds even more layers of flavor. Softened butter is swirled with red pepper jam for a tangy waffle spread and hot sauce is drizzled over top. Serve up these Southern-inspired plates for breakfast (or dinner!) and enjoy a savory-sweet meal with a down-home feel.
